blueprint.description:
This comes from
https://factorioprints.com/view/-MJURcCFL-9L_cbihLys
with no changes (as it's my own blueprint).

Noxy's Waterfill Required!
(I may create a landfill-only version if people really want it)

Power switch is OFF by default though it's okay to turn it on after a clean lay-down of the blueprint.

There will be a steel chest with three reactors at the construction site.  These need to be manually placed over the three roboports down the reactor row once construction is complete.
blueprint.label: Nuclear (10GW)
